v0.0.1:
Correct Meta for iOS and Android
Dynamic CSS link
iOS6 Header
iOS6 Normal text
Do not remove elastic scrolling. Want to be able to scroll down if there is a lot of content. Look at iOS Settings, it elastically scrolls!

v0.0.2:

Notes:
Invariants: Sections must be given a class of levelN. Sections cannot mutate based on user interaction.


